data.description: Remodeled move in ready 3 bed 2 bath right in Cripple Creek. Great opportunity for affordable living in the wonderful Colorado mountain town of Cripple Creek. Beautifully remodeled kitchen with new cabinets, stainless steel appliances, butcher block countertops and double basin sink. Master bedroom with private master bath including dual sinks. Both baths are updated with new sinks, showers and accessories. All new flooring. All new LED lighting. All new windows. Fresh paint inside and out. Laundry hookups. All living facilities on one level. Incredible mountain views. No HOA. Walking distance to all the amenities of historic Cripple Creek. Come see today!
